# Repository License Summary

This repository uses a split license.

## Code

Source code in `demo/*.js`, `demo/*.css`, `demo/*.html`, `presentation/*.html`, `presentation/*.css`, and public-safe configuration examples in `repro/configs/` is released under the MIT License.

See `LICENSE-CODE-MIT.md`.

## Documentation, Reports, Presentation, and Assets

Text, reports, paper drafts, presentation content, screenshots, visual/demo assets, and explanatory replay content are released under Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International.

See `LICENSE-DOCS-ASSETS-CC-BY-NC-4.0.md`.

## Third-Party Files

Third-party libraries keep their original licenses. In particular, `demo/vendor/phaser.min.js` is not relicensed by this repository.

## Note

This summary is provided for repository clarity and is not legal advice.
